'''天主教卡西諾山自治會院區'''是天主教在義大利一個[[自治會院區|自治會院區]]。此自治會院區直屬[[聖座|聖座]]，是[[天主教會|天主教會]]現存的十一個自治會院區之一。會院區始於529年，[[聖本篤|聖本篤]]在[[卡西諾山|卡西諾山]]建立了隱修院。

2014年10月23日，會院以外的轄地轉至索拉-阿奎諾-蓬泰科爾沃教區，教區亦因而改名為[[天主教索拉-卡西諾-阿奎諾-蓬泰科爾沃教區|索拉-卡西諾-阿奎諾-蓬泰科爾沃教區]]。<ref name="Vatican20141023">{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 23.10.2014 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2014/10/23/0784/01660.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-07-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190715082624/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2014/10/23/0784/01660.html |archivedate=2019-07-15 |language=it |date=2014-10-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

自治會院區於2004年時有79,000名教友、五十三個堂區和六十八名司鐸。現任院長為{{link-it|陶納多·奧利亞里|Donato Ogliari}}，[[本篤會|O.S.B.]]<ref name="Vatican20141023" />，榮休院長為{{link-it|伯多祿·托維雷利|Pietro Vittorelli}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 12.06.2013 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2013/06/12/0377/00862.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-02-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200216181453/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2013/06/12/0377/00862.html |archivedate=2020-02-16 |language=it |date=2013-06-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

